{"type":"article","id":21157,"title":"莫迪亲赴拉达克前线视察","uid":1275,"topics":[9737,9346],"contents":"印度官员们说，总理莫迪今天（3日）前往印中两国边境地区拉达克（Ladakh）进行访问。<br>\n<br>\n据路透社报道，印度官员们指出，莫迪是在由印度国防参谋长拉瓦特（Bipin Rawat）和陆军总司令纳拉瓦尼（Manoj Mukund Naravane）陪同下前往这个喜马拉雅地区。<br>\n<br>\n印度亚洲国际新闻通讯社（ANI）的照片显示，莫迪在拉达克一个军事基地会见了当地部队。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2cnJ2M7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2cnJ2M7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2cnJ2M7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/2BqY4sn.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2BqY4sn.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2BqY4sn.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NI6SIma.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NI6SIma.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NI6SIma.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-04","agreeCount":10,"discussionCount":0}